{"tid":1012666,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［幾時禁用埋USB手指？］海豹糞便樣本中發現USB記憶體","createTime":"2019-02-07T17:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T18:17:09.000Z","uid":49727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cfd2c7e8295fef372eec05d2c4825e3b4c5d27","tid":1012666,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-47155847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-47155847&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bcr9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=f71fc0ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-47155847&h=0629af38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-47155847</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/A617/production/_105491524_leopardseal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2FA617%2Fproduction%2F_105491524_leopardseal.jpg&h=c3c9bba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究人員在一份被收集用作科學研究的海豹糞便樣本中，發現一支充滿旅行照片的USB記憶體。<br />\n<br />\n該樣本已被雪藏超過一年，用以研究新西蘭海域海豹的健康及飲食習慣。而該支USB記憶體運作完全正常，內藏有一輯海獅的照片及一對海豹母子在水中嬉戲的影片。<br />\n<br />\n糞便樣本由當地一名獸醫提交，他在新西蘭南島城市因弗卡吉爾的Oreti海灘觀察一頭生病的海豹。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭國立水與大氣研究所在網站上表示，「該枝USB記憶體保存狀態頗佳，『尤其以它所經歷過的來說』。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/niwa_nz/status/1092610541401587712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fniwa_nz%2Fstatus%2F1092610541401587712&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bcr9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=24a3f414\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fniwa_nz%2Fstatus%2F1092610541401587712&h=9340bd50\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/niwa_nz/status/1092610541401587712</a><br />\n<br />\n研究人員發現記憶體內藏有大量生態短片。不過動物吃下這樣的塑膠到體內，引起他們的關注。<br />\n<br />\n「在這些南極洲動物的體內找到塑膠，情況非常令人擔憂。」義工祖迪華倫說。而目前仍未找到USB記憶體的主人。<br />\n<br />\n研究中心稱失主如果想拿回USB記憶體，可以收集新的海豹糞便作為交換。<br />\n<br />\n「對這些海豹了解愈深，對海豹保育工作愈有益處。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海豹好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環保撚幾時爭取禁用USB手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5461f25da06c8610ec3ce088767c5333235bdffe","tid":1012666,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"邊間廠嘅手指咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}